        <div class="panel-body">
            <p>
                The inventory of the Institute for Criminology in Tübingen is mainly focused on criminological literature in the German language. Contrary to the Institute for Criminology, the Tübingen University library mainly acquires literature in foreign languages. Besides criminological literature, the University library also tries to acquire relevant literature of fundamental and reference sciences. More information is available in the <a href="<?=$this->url('content-page', ['page' => 'acquisition'])?>">acquisition profile</a>. An overview of recently acquired monographs can be found in the <a href="http://biber3.ub.uni-tuebingen.de/nelol/cgi-bin/neuerw.pl?loc=krim" target="_blank">list of new acquisitions</a> of the Criminological Information Service.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

